We'd like to introduce you to Melanie, our featured Citizen of the Week!<br><br>Melanie has been a citizen of Millsberry since April 27th, 2007. That makes almost two years that Mel has been enjoying the wide world of Millsberry, and she's settled in quite nicely.<br><br><a href="http://dev.millsberry.com/home/?user=brennybearxoxo"><a href='/home/?user=brennybearxoxo'>57711-B Aldan Lake</a></a> is where Melanie calls home. And the Lakeview neighborhood has been good to her so far. Melanie loves to sail, so being close to the lake is a perfect fit. <br><br>Another thing the lake is good for is reading. Melanie has spent many afternoons sitting by the water, nose buried in one of her favorite books.<br><br>Melanie describes herself as very compassionate. Of course, it takes someone who's compassionate to save the galaxy. No wonder she has a trophy for Galactic Defender! <br><br>When she's not protecting the far reaches of outer space, Melanie is likely solving a mystery or two. Playing detective is another one of her favorite activities. <br><br>Melanie has also collected top honors in <a href="http://dev.millsberry.com/gamepages/flashgame_ctp.phtml?game_id=160">Home Run Derby</a>, <a href="http://dev.millsberry.com/gamepages/flashgame_ctp.phtml?game_id=484">Tricky Touchdown</a>, and <a href="http://dev.millsberry.com/gamepages/flashgame_ctp.phtml?game_id=486">Kai's Surfari</a>. And, with a trophy for Batman's Battle Rolls, you can be sure that she's is one of the "Good Guys!"<br><br>Melanie's trophy collection is rivaled only by her great taste in music. When it's time to get down, Melanie enjoys grooving to the sounds of pop, punk, and world music. <br><br>Next time you see Melanie, be sure to congratulate her and thank her for being such an outstanding citizen!</div>
